Yes, I remember one - rabbit especially - an old man at the end killed it, 'cos we wanted something for dinner you see. I was upset over that one. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid4728504 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid14774904\charrsid12714737 You said you did do gardening?
